    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately not assessed per MRL 2 scoping. Grid convergence index for the hemolysis QoI is within the 5% acceptance threshold. Validation data span the full CPB operating range and demonstrate RH < 1 at all simulated conditions. The credibility assessment supports regulatory submission for the Class II CPB device.",
